der-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: s=
olid; background-color: #ccc;"> discussed yesterday</a>, the LME has suspen=
ded reporting an =E2=80=9COfficial Price=E2=80=9D while it does this weird =
slow walk back to the correct price. I suppose part of the rationale for th=
is is that, since the limit-down prices reported on the LME this week are i=
n some obvious sense not =E2=80=9Ccorrect,=E2=80=9D it would be strange to =
report them as official prices. But the LME=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27061747.258600/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubG1lLmN=
