omatic trading pauses when prices move very far very fast, on the theory th=
at moves like that might be =E2=80=9Cwrong=E2=80=9D and so investors should=
 take some time to think about things. The LME did that in a more manual an=
d=C2=A0dramatic way, suspending trading for a week.</p><p style=3D"margin: =
16px 0;">Or you could=C2=A0<em>retroactively cancel the trades you think we=
re crazy</em>, which is a very drastic move and not really recommended; aga=
in the LME did that, and it got a lot of criticism for doing so. In general=
 I am <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27061747.258=
600/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMTQ=
vbmlja2VsLWJsb3d1cC1tYWRlLWEtbG90LW9mLXRyb3VibGU_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDMxNzIyX01PTk=
VZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09M=
jIwMzE3JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5ade8815" =
itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"c=
olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color:=
 #ccc;"> sympathetic to the critics</a> =E2=80=94=C2=A0market prices are ma=
rket prices and you should not tear up trades between willing buyers and wi=
lling sellers because you don=E2=80=99t like the price or because it is bad=
 for a few favored market participants =E2=80=94=C2=A0but I can see the LME=
=E2=80=99s side as well. It=E2=80=99s an exchange to set the price of nicke=
l, it wants to get the price right, and if the price is wildly wrong it wil=
l be tempted to fix it.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The point is =
that if you are doing all of these quite drastic things it is because you a=
re very confident that the price has gotten very wrong! You have a strong o=
pinion that differs from the market price on the screen, and you are confid=
ent that your opinion is right, the market is wrong, and you should overrid=
e the market.=C2=A0If you have that confidence, it seems strange to reopen =
trading a week later=C2=A0and say =E2=80=9Cwell, this price is wrong, but w=
